{"tid":1510111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"開學之後，教師係一條戰線","createTime":"2019-08-27T05:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T01:19:32.000Z","uid":278052,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"d978c72980244f3a646bec54d1d0f46fe16f8881","tid":1510111,"uid":278052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:23:19.000Z","msg":"各位中小學老師<br />\n<br />\n係開學之後，你地一定會受到教育局、校長、校董會、家教會等等制肘，禁止你地談論政治，甚至你哋會因為立場問題而遭受各程度懲罰，目的係希望老師禁聲甚或乎滅聲，令民主自由種子無法繼續傳播，令運動污名化。<br />\n<br />\n壓力會好大，但係請求你地要無時無刻，記住係前線既年輕人企係子彈面前都無畏無懼，為你地、為你地既子女、為大家既香港，抗爭到現在，流既血多不勝數。<br />\n<br />\n希望你地對良心負責仼，不要屈服於強權底下。<br />\n<br />\n老師影響力非常非常之大，你地唔會知受你地熏陶成長嘅學生，會運用自己嘅影響力再去影響幾多人，你播一粒種子，將來可能係一塊田園。<br />\n<br />\n誠懇呼籲各位教師，開學之後守護我地下一代既思想，令佢地分黑白，明事非，而非做政府想佢地要成為既人。"},{"pid":"06de19fe6ea148f028ee1d9839101ca5eccd0e16","tid":1510111,"uid":33930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi0PYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=bc39611b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi0PYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=d53934b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi0PYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=2239d972\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"168337eed2acd73ff46c9356f4945d6d15a32606","tid":1510111,"uid":278052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:24:48.000Z","msg":"p牌推唔郁，但係好希望各位教師睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23252cd652853b0b55f86b7163d0f65277ab0b8d","tid":1510111,"uid":278052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:26:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"113468d5b9650da249b29cad461d07d93ccf9ad4","tid":1510111,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:29:38.000Z","msg":"推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d983eb8c53c2bbe8208b065a76c4ab5554789b02","tid":1510111,"uid":274732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:30:00.000Z","msg":"琴日開教職員大會<br />\n講明所有老師職員如出席任何示威遊行活動<br />\n校董會會立即辭退老師教席<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地為我彈子彈<br />\n我為你地包到實繼續上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339cc0ee31b9e893f0978b13eff100cdceb30d83","tid":1510111,"uid":278052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d983eb8c53c2bbe8208b065a76c4ab5554789b02","tid":1510111,"uid":274732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:30:00.000Z","msg":"琴日開教職員大會<br />\n講明所有老師職員如出席任何示威遊行活動<br />\n校董會會立即辭退老師教席<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地為我彈子彈<br />\n我為你地包到實繼續上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:31:49.000Z","msg":"已經預見到開學之後一定嚴重干預老師嘅言行<br />\n希望各位老師頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738498756926ee1023ecc0017a88155b6cf67ad9","tid":1510111,"uid":274732,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"339cc0ee31b9e893f0978b13eff100cdceb30d83","tid":1510111,"uid":278052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"s